    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fight for the future starts now. Fight with or against your friends with crazy sci-fi tech, innovative mechanics, and a classic yet colorful retro feel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIGHT YOUR WAY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duel it out with or against your friends  in 1v1 Fight, Training Mode, and 4-Player Free For All and Team Battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155390/extras/61189ab607c452ecdda56484f6cd03f0.avif?t=1764197964\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155390/extras_big/61189ab607c452ecdda56484f6cd03f0.webp?t=1764197964 width=1560 height=975 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VARIOUS FIGHTER</strong> <strong>COMPLEXITIES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All fighters can be played at different complexities to either simplify or expand upon the fighter's mechanics. MODERATE is the intended way to play, but SIMPLE offers a easier experience for new players and ADVANCED offers more depth to look into. Whether you are a casual or competitive player, everyone can enjoy the same fighters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155390/extras/f3b386fcd314ff971bf8787dee1a6b4c.avif?t=1764197964\" width=1440 height=367 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW REMEDIES, NEW CHALLENGES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many ways the game addresses approachability, such as simple inputs, holding down inputs, and all moves being juggle friendly. But do not think this is a watered down experience! Not only are there strong universal mechanics like canceling and the<i> Vigor System</i>, but every character has special, unique mechanics to add high-level difficulty back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155390/extras/e00eaf354a2adef44c9d608dbb1c534c.avif?t=1764197964\" width=1439 height=738 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try out this crazy new fighter today!</p>",
